This Health Screening is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of a qualified health provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Health screening results will be reviewed for the sole purpose of gaining access to our offices and confidentiality will be maintained.
